title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update -  Sim Update VIII - Only 3 days until available!
description:
Only 3 days until Sim Update VIII is available if everything goes as planned. After the beta period which started almost 2 weeks ago it is time for the final version to be released on Monday. During the beta 2 interim fixes were released with the latest one only 16 hours ago. The version number of Sim Update VIII will likely be 1.23.12.0 if no new versions are discovered.
